title: Host Out of Town Guests Overnight in the Guest Suite
posting_body: ['The Durham features just the right blend of charm and the ideal location for your next home.', 'Our community offers a variety of spacious apartment homes ranging from one-bedroom to three-bedroom floor plans.', 'Residents enjoy breathtaking views from our balconies, generous closet space, quartz counters, plank flooring and much, much more!', 'The Durham is nestled in the suburb of Edina with easy access to several major highways.', '-Studio+ Highlighting Wellbeats!', 'Offering a Variety of On-Demand Exercise Programs', '-Package Concierge Offering 24-Hour Access to Packages', '-Large, Glass-Enclosed Indoor Pool, Sauna and Steam Room Open Year Round', '-Well Equipped Tech Center with Mac and PC Computers and Multi-Function Printer', '-Quality-crafted cabinetry with under cabinet lighting', '-Concrete construction creates acoustically sound units', '-Payments', 'Accepted: Credit Card, Cash via MoneyGram, Apple Pay and FREE E-Check', '-The Board Room is Perfect for Private Meetings', '-Moen Align bathroom collection in a chrome finish for a modern look', '-Designer tile backsplash with elegant quartz countertops', '-Three, Lighted Tennis Courts Featuring a Versacourt System', '-Host Out of Town Guests Overnight in the Guest Suite', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>']
